import * as React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Grid2 as Grid,
  Card,
  CardHeader,
  CardContent,
  Typography,
  Chip,
  Stack,
  Button,
  Divider,
  Skeleton,
} from '@mui/material';
// import { useGetOverviewQuery } from "@/store/api"; // 你自己的 RTK Query
// import { LineChart, Line, XAxis, YAxis, Tooltip, ResponsiveContainer, PieChart, Pie, Cell, BarChart, Bar } from "recharts";
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';

export default function Overview(): React.ReactElement {
  const navigate = useNavigate();
  // const { data, isLoading, isError, refetch } = useGetOverviewQuery({ range: "7d" });
  const isLoading = false; // 先占位
  const isError = false;
  const data = undefined as any;

  return (
    <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 2 }}>
      {/* 顶部工具条（日期范围/筛选 可后补） */}
      <Stack direction="row" alignItems="center" spacing={1}>
        <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ flex: 1 }}>
          Overview
        </Typography>
        <Button size="small" variant="outlined" onClick={() => navigate('/live')}>
          Go Live
        </Button>
        <Button size="small" onClick={() => navigate('/violations')}>
          All Violations
        </Button>
      </Stack>

      {/* KPI 区 */}
      <Grid container spacing={2}>
        {[
          { label: 'Violations (Today)', value: '—', change: '+0%' },
          { label: 'Active Alerts', value: '—' },
          { label: 'Cameras Online', value: '—/—' },
          { label: 'Uptime', value: '—%' },
          { label: 'MTTA', value: '— s' },
          { label: 'MTTR', value: '— s' },
        ].map((k, i) => (
          <Grid key={i} size={{ xs: 12, sm: 6, md: 4, lg: 2 }}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  {k.label}
                </Typography>
                <Stack direction="row" alignItems="baseline" spacing={1}>
                  <Typography variant="h5">{k.value}</Typography>
                  {k.change && (
                    <Chip size="small" label={k.change} color="success" variant="outlined" />
                  )}
                </Stack>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        ))}
      </Grid>

      <Grid container spacing={2}>
        {/* 违规趋势 */}
        <Grid size={{ xs: 12, md: 8 }}>
          <Card sx={{ height: 360, display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
            <CardHeader title="Violations (7d)" />
            <Divider />
            <CardContent sx={{ flex: 1, minHeight: 0 }}>
              {isLoading ? (
                <Skeleton variant="rounded" height="100%" />
              ) : (
                <Box sx={{ height: 280, bgcolor: 'background.default' }}>
                  {/* <ResponsiveContainer width="100%" height="100%">
                    <LineChart data={data?.trend}>
                      <XAxis dataKey="ts" hide />
                      <YAxis allowDecimals={false} />
                      <Tooltip />
                      <Line type="monotone" dataKey="violations" strokeWidth={2} dot={false} />
                    </LineChart>
                  </ResponsiveContainer> */}
                </Box>
              )}
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* 类型分布 */}
        <Grid size={{ xs: 12, md: 4 }}>
          <Card sx={{ height: 360, display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
            <CardHeader title="By Type" />
            <Divider />
            <CardContent sx={{ flex: 1, minHeight: 0 }}>
              {isLoading ? (
                <Skeleton variant="rounded" height="100%" />
              ) : (
                <Stack spacing={1}>
                  {/* <ResponsiveContainer width="100%" height={240}>
                    <PieChart>
                      <Pie data={data?.byType} dataKey="count" nameKey="type" outerRadius={100}>
                        {data?.byType.map((_, idx) => <Cell key={idx} />)}
                      </Pie>
                      <Tooltip />
                    </PieChart>
                  </ResponsiveContainer> */}
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                    Top risky types in last 7d
                  </Typography>
                </Stack>
              )}
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* 最近违规 */}
        <Grid size={{ xs: 12, md: 7 }}>
          <Card sx={{ height: 420, display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
            <CardHeader
              title="Recent Violations"
              action={
                <Button size="small" onClick={() => navigate('/violations')}>
                  View all
                </Button>
              }
            />
            <Divider />
            <CardContent sx={{ flex: 1, overflow: 'auto' }}>
              {isLoading ? (
                <Stack spacing={1}>
                  {Array.from({ length: 6 }).map((_, i) => (
                    <Skeleton key={i} height={42} />
                  ))}
                </Stack>
              ) : (
                <Stack divider={<Divider flexItem />} spacing={1}>
                  {/* data?.recentViolations.map(v => ( */}
                  <Stack key="demo" direction="row" spacing={2} alignItems="center" sx={{ py: 1 }}>
                    <Chip size="small" label="HIGH" color="error" />
                    <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ minWidth: 120 }}>
                      12:03:18
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ flex: 1 }}>
                      No Helmet
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                      Cam-12
                    </Typography>
                  </Stack>
                  {/* )) */}
                </Stack>
              )}
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* 设备健康 */}
        <Grid size={{ xs: 12, md: 5 }}>
          <Card sx={{ height: 420, display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
            <CardHeader title="Cameras Health" />
            <Divider />
            <CardContent sx={{ flex: 1, overflow: 'auto' }}>
              {isLoading ? (
                <Stack spacing={1}>
                  {Array.from({ length: 6 }).map((_, i) => (
                    <Skeleton key={i} height={42} />
                  ))}
                </Stack>
              ) : (
                <Stack divider={<Divider flexItem />} spacing={1}>
                  {/* data?.cameras.map(cam => ( */}
                  <Stack key="cam1" direction="row" spacing={2} alignItems="center" sx={{ py: 1 }}>
                    <Chip size="small" label="Online" color="success" />
                    <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ flex: 1 }}>
                      Entrance North
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                      FPS 25
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                      2.1 Mbps
                    </Typography>
                  </Stack>
                  {/* )) */}
                </Stack>
              )}
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
}
